HEADWORD: Demigorge
<hw>Dem"i*gorge`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>demi- gorge</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Fort.)</fld> <def>Half the gorge,
or entrance into a bastion, taken from the angle of the flank to the
center of the bastion.</def>⟦br⟧
